data.description: Amazing town home, pet friendly and perfect fit for a small family. Gorgeous lake view with sparkling water fountain. Spacious Screened back patio.  Freshly painted 2/2, 2 huge bedrooms with en suite bathrooms.  Newly remodeled half bath with gorgeous light fixture.  Large kitchen with white cabinets, stainless steel appliances.   Samsung Washer & Dryer.  Home is in great condition and well kept.  Seller is motivated. Price is Negotiable.    Newly installed Water Heater.
